{
  "texts": [
    "XPS was performed using a Thermo Fisher Scientific XPS NEXSA spectrometer with a monochromated Al K α X-ray source operating at 1486.6 eV.",
    "XPS survey measurements used a pass energy of 200 eV and an energy resolution of 1 eV.",
    "High-resolution XPS spectra were collected using a pass energy of 50 eV and an energy resolution of 0.1 eV.",
    "The analyzed area was 200 µm 2, and a flood gun was used for charge compensation.",
    "Optical measurements."
  ]
}